race.comment: MAKING MEMORIES (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at Q Lakeside following on from a second place finish (19.95) there the start prior. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Has ability and is a key runner. NOT THE DEPUTY (7) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his dynamic win three back, getting around this track over 350m in 18.94. Has the ability and can find winning form again. TIBETAN BELLE (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 350m (19.50). One of the main contenders. TYPHOON VINNIE (6) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.
